80→    "- Set severity to conflict/warning/info based on urgency.",
81→    "",
82→    "## Output",
83→    "Return strict JSON only (no markdown).",
84→    "Match this schema exactly: summary, suggestions, updated, discarded, observations_created.",
85→    "If no suggestions remain after dedup, return suggestions: [].",
